# Fast prompts

## Homepage spacing/layout

```
@src/components/home/AiDesignHomepage.tsx
Increase [section] padding by [N]px. Only that section.
```

## Coco Care spacing/layout (pick the chapter file)

```
@src/components/project/cococare/chapters/ResearchSection.tsx
[change]. Minimal diff. Do not edit other chapters.
```

Files: `ResearchSection`, `DefineSection`, `IdeateSection`, `PrototypeSection`, `TestSection`, or `ProjectHero.tsx`.

## Coco Care copy only

```
@src/lib/cocoCareContent.ts
Update [field]: "[new text]". Do not touch CocoCarePage.tsx.
```

## Global tokens / shared CSS

```
@src/styles.css @src/lib/designSystem.ts
[change]. Prefer existing CSS variables/classes.
```

Never ask to preview in Cursor browser — user refreshes Safari/Chrome on localhost:5173.
